{"'Arrays must have the same length'":"E0","`HTTP ${response.status}`":"E1","'No response body to stream'":"E2","'string notation required for auto precision.'":"E3","INPUT_ERROR":"E4","FINALIZE_ERROR":"E5","'Illegal argument ' + message":"E6","'Invalid data'":"E7","'The amount of data is too big to be stored in a QR Code'":"E8","'\\n' +\n      'The chosen QR Code version cannot contain this amount of data.\\n' +\n      'Minimum version required to store current data is: ' + bestVersion + '.\\n'":"E9","'No input text'":"E10","'Encoder not initialized'":"E11","'\"' + data + '\"' +\n      ' cannot be encoded with mode ' + Mode.toString(mode) +\n      '.\\n Suggested mode is: ' + Mode.toString(bestMode)":"E12","'\"version\" cannot be null or undefined'":"E13","'\"version\" should be in range from 1 to 40'":"E14","'\"toSJISFunc\" is not a valid function.'":"E15","'Invalid QR Code version'":"E16","ed[0]":"E17","msg || ec[ind]":"E18","'FetchError'":"E19","`HTTP error! status: ${response.status}`":"E20","msg.error":"E21","'Invalid JSON response from server'":"E22","'The provider is not valid.'":"E23","msg":"E24","\"Cannot find module '\"+o+\"'\"":"E25","'resolver must be a function'":"E26","'Cannot resolve promise with itself'":"E27","'must be an array'":"E28","\"Cannot call a class as a function\"":"E29","'Failed to get type for BinaryArray'":"E30","'Unkown type: ' + type":"E31","\"Can't call config() after localforage \" + 'has been used.'":"E32","'Database version must be a number.'":"E33","'Custom driver not compliant; see ' + 'https://mozilla.github.io/localForage/#definedriver'":"E34","'Method ' + methodName + ' is not implemented by the current driver'":"E35","'Driver not found.'":"E36","'No available storage method found.'":"E37"}